## D-04: JSON Schemas

Declarative validation for module metadata and security profiles.

### 1. Manifest Schema
**File**: [module_manifest.schema.json](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/schemas/module_manifest.schema.json)
Enforces semver versioning, [.py](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/core/main.py) entrypoints, and required security lists.

### 2. Capabilities Schema
**File**: [capabilities.schema.json](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/schemas/capabilities.schema.json)
Restricts modules to a predefined enum of kernel capabilities (e.g., `STORAGE_READ`, `EVENT_PUBLISH`).

### 3. Permissions Schema
**File**: [module_permissions.schema.json](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/schemas/module_permissions.schema.json)
Validates the module-specific permission grants.

